div1.p: In the District Court for the First Judicial District for the Territory of Washington the Territory of Washington to James McAuliff Sherrif of Walla Walla County

Whereas an affidavit hath this day been made before me by F. Fetter the lawful guardian father of Susannah Fetter setting forth that over Eugene Crowne & L Fetter unlawfully restrained said Susannah Fetter a minor child of her liberty and are about to transport the said Susannah Fetter beyond the jurisdiction of this court before process case served on E Crowne & L Fetter – Now therfore James McCauliff Sherrif of the County of Walla Walla
are hereby commanded fourth with to arrest the said Susannah Fetter and bring her before the Hon. J E judge dist court 1 st jud dis w. t. chambers there to be dealt with according to law
In Witness whereof I have hereunto set my hand and affixed the official Seal of said Court this the 27th day of May AD 1869.
B.J. Wyche Clerk of the District Court of the First Judicial Distict of Washington Territory.
